<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/the-national-lottery-community-fund> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The National Lottery Community Fund awards money raised by National Lottery players to communities across the UK, working with local groups and UK-wide charities, enabling people and communities to thrive. The National Lottery Community Fund is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
